cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GT, cs.MA, cs.CY 

This paper deals with recommendation systems and their exploration-exploitation tradeoffs, which are common topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also introduces a model for the recommendation system, which can be categorized under game theory (cs.GT) and multi-agent systems (cs.MA). Finally, the paper discusses the ethical considerations of the recommendation system, which can be related to computer ethics (cs.CY).
